      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation performed on the nominal geometry. GCI for RH index: 3.1% (coarse-to-medium), 1.4% (medium-to-fine). Fine mesh (4.2M cells) adopted for all production runs. Discretization error is adequately characterised at Gradation 2."
