      "rationale": "In-vitro tests conducted with bovine blood at 37 °C, haematocrit 33±2%. CFD boundary conditions set to match mean measured values. Fluid viscosity and density verified against rheometry data. Condition matching satisfies Gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
